The evidence with the title 'Median income jumps 5.2% in 2015 - sep. 13, 2016 ' says Sep 13, 2016  ... After years of watching their incomes go nowhere, America's middle class finally got a big raise last year.  ... Median income: the jump in median income was one of the largest annual increases Census has recorded.  ... Some 43.1 million Americans were in poverty last year, 3.5 million less than in 2014. 
